  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1948206/" class="title-link">写给大家的中国美术史：果然是写给大家的</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1948206"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1063899/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1063899-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1063899/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">周六我要休息</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-04-06"
      class="main-meta">2009-04-06 18:00:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1948206_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   读得很快。比如今天中午先生打电话的功夫，我就从唐代一直读到元代了；花儿移了盆，接着读，然后就读完了。果然是写给大家看的。  语言浅显，不掉书袋，常常用如同跟孩子讲话般的语气说婉转的设问或反问，或惊讶的话。比如“其实，我们的老祖先就是用这些自然的石头，泥土，花...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1948206/#comments">(11回应)</a>
