  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1698904/" class="title-link">怎样的美术史是“大家的美术史”?</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1698904"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/heshanyun/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1173150-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/heshanyun/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">蓝色透心</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-02-17"
      class="main-meta">2009-02-17 17:54:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1698904_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      这几日翻的是《写给大家的中国美术史》，刚好做研修班的会务杂事，这样的美书自然是翻得顺手。作者是台湾学者蒋勋，文笔轻松，摆脱了以往“～～史”的沉闷，正如他自己在前言中所言，要摒弃“吊书袋子”的习惯，写一本人人都能念的“中国美术史”，让追寻美成为每一个人都...

